      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku mau bertanya apa kamu pernah mengalami mimpi aneh?
