  - dialogueID: Miiyu Bulan 4 event part 3
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Oh iya Pemain apa kamu udah siap nanti?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Siap apa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Memang nya ada apa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu bener-bener tidak tau?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kan 2 bulan lagi kita UTS
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu serius
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu tidak bohong kan?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu serius
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kenapa aku harus berbohong
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Berarti kita harus belajar bareng buat UTS nanti?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Biar lebih gampang kalau ada yang salah bisa saling bantu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"(Kaget)" kamu mau belajar bareng bersama aku?'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Tentu aja kita kan udah pernah menggerjakan tugas bareng
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Apa jangan-jangan kamu udah punya rencana dengan orang lain?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"(Kaget dan senang)" E-eh?!, engga ko aku baru di ajak sama
        kamu doang'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "B-boleh banget\u2026 aku malah senang sekali. Kalau sama kamu,
        mungkin aku bisa lebih semangat"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau gitu, kita harus tentuin tempat dan waktunya, ya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Gimana kalau perpustakaan seperti biasa
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Boleh sih tapi kan pasti akan ramai
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau begitu gimana pas selesai jam sekolah kita ke perpustakaan
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku yakin akan sepi dan sekolah di tutup hingga sore harus nya
        kita punya beberapa jam untuk belajar bareng
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu kelihatan nya semangat banget
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Ma...af ini pertama kali nya aku belajar bareng sama orang lain
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: justru aku senang,Tapi coba aku pikir kan dulu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
