    - sentenceText: Kalo di pikir-pikir lagi aku jadi semakin gugup
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: Miyu Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 04073754593a83042b561d10c04a146c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Seharus nya kita udah siap untuk ulangan UTS nanti
