  - dialogueID: Miiyu Bulan 9 event part 3
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: '"Di saat itu pemain sadar betapa indah nya Miyu"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu tidak bisa menyerah, ya?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6607ce4ce739c854d9e1b109532dc366, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Tidak akan
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kenapa? Apa Kamu tidak lelah menghadapi orang yang terus bersembunyi?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4d7d748f33700184ca3579347d840f75, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Tidak. Karena aku tahu, di balik diam itu, ada seseorang yang
        menunggu dipahami
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku takut. Takut jika aku membuka diri, aku akan kehilangan semuanya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1abb11c22fdd1bc4ab13db5786ae6105, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kau tidak kehilangan apa pun saat jujur. Kau justru mulai menemukan
        dirimu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku tidak muu sendirian lagi
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 62c5824a06a283147abbfb9ed55d5d5c, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Maka jangan
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Apa Bolehkah aku tetap di sisimu\u2026 meskipun aku sering diam?"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: fbf31dce9f00e11408eaaa66d4e0ed1f, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Miyu
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 28f6491ce9a067540b77ce056ffd717c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Justru dalam diam itulah aku menemukan kedamaian mu itu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
