  - dialogueID: Yumi Bulan 4 event part 3
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Oh iya Pemain
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Apa kamu udah siap nanti Pemain
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Siap apa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Emang bakalan ada apa nanti?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Seriusan kamu ga tau
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Haah oh iya kamu anak baru di sekolah ini
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Sebener nya 2 bulan lagi kita bakalan UTS
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Seriusan ko aku tidak tau
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu harus nya tau soal nya ini udah di pertengahan materi pembelajaran
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Wah hebat juga ya kamu Yumi
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Hump ini mah bukan masalah buat ku
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Berarti kita harus belajar bareng buat UTS nanti?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Biar lebih gampang kalau ada yang salah bisa saling bantu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu serius mau belajar bareng bersama ku?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Tentu aja kita kan udah pernah menggerjakan tugas bareng
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Apa jangan-jangan kamu udah punya rencana dengan orang lain?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Tidak,hanya saja ini pertama kali nya aku di ajak belajar bareng
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: ya kalo kamu maksa aku ga akan tolak
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau gitu, kita harus tentuin tempat dan waktunya, ya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Bagai mana kalo di kelas saja sesudah sekolah selesai
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Seharus nya sekolah tutup sampai sore
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Bukan nya Kelas akan di kunci setelah jam pelajaran terakhir
        selesai?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau itu tenang saja aku bisa meminta kunci ke guru walikelas
        kita untuk menetap di kelas lebih lama
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu kelihatan nya semangat banget
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Jangan salah paham dulu ya,aku melakukan ini bukan nya aku perhatian
        atau apa ya Hump
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: Yumi Close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Tapi aku pikir pikir dulu ya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7f5483e24d566cc4b9ccf586e5935cf1, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: '"Terima tawaran"'
      nextDialogueID: Yumi Bulan 4 event part 4
      moodTargetHeroine: 2
      moodChangeAmount: 3
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 1
