  - dialogueID: Yumi Bulan 9 event part 3
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: '"Saat aku melihat Yumi memgeluarkan air mata"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Apa kamu tak apa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Kenapa kamu repot-repot? Aku tuh\u2026 cuman  gadis yang keras
        kepala tau!"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 101963f1236a72b4aa4207062d27fa1f, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Karena aku menyukaimu apa adanya, keras kepala dan semuanya
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: '"(Yumi terdiam. Cahaya kembang api memantul di matanya.)"'
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Kamu itu\u2026 benar-benar tidak tahu malu dan aneh ya"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: caa06b8e7f53fc445911b491f077a3a7, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau harus malu demi membuatmu tersenyum, aku rela ko
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: "Aku tidak pandai mengungkapkan perasaan. Tapi\u2026 kalau aku
        berkata \u2018terima kasih\u2019, apakah itu cukup?"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a3773dee4332bf46a107516d777c7be, type: 3}
      speakingCharacterKey: Yumi
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c267365f8615d9945befceb57bf88228, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: Lebih dari cukup, Yumi
