  - dialogueID: Hikari Bulan 6 event part 2
    dialogueSteps:
    - sentenceText: Kalo gitu ayo kita jalan Pemain
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 04073754593a83042b561d10c04a146c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kenapa kamu yang tiba tiba yang memimpin
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 04073754593a83042b561d10c04a146c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Emang nya kamu tau rumah ku di mana?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 04073754593a83042b561d10c04a146c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Hehe.... engga
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 04073754593a83042b561d10c04a146c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku cuman bersemangat aja
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 04073754593a83042b561d10c04a146c, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Rumah ku sebener nya dekat dengan sekolah
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cd8e6cf153780c4479a61f1c32f41885, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Saat kamu lihat taman di sana kamu langsung bisa lihat rumah
        ku
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cd8e6cf153780c4479a61f1c32f41885, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Jangan bilang taman yang ada perosotan nya itu?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cd8e6cf153780c4479a61f1c32f41885, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Iya yang itu dan depan nya rumah ku memang nya kenapa?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1426c481b1eb2e54d909793ac1fc1184, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Aku dulu sering main disini soal nya ini tempat faforit ku dulu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cd8e6cf153780c4479a61f1c32f41885, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Waw aku ga nyangka kalau kamu pernah kesini
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1426c481b1eb2e54d909793ac1fc1184, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kalau gitu langsung masuk saja ke rumah ku dan langsung kekamar
        saja
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1426c481b1eb2e54d909793ac1fc1184, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Jadi ini Kamar mu Pemain
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Oh iya Pemain aku mau memberi salam dulu sama keluarga mu
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Owh kamu ga usah kawatir orang tua ku hari ini pulang larut
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Jadi kita hanya berdua di rumah ini
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu nakal juga ya Pemain"(Dengan muka jail)"
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Close up
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Kamu ga lupa kan kita ngapain hari ini
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Pemain
      activeCharacterKeys: 
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    - sentenceText: Makan dan tidur?
      voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
      speakingCharacterKey: Hikari
      activeCharacterKeys: Hikari Biasa
      iconSprite: {fileID: 0}
      backgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 99517b0d7c32efa49a7bc7e10784b0c0, type: 3}
      changeBackground: 1
    choices:
    - choiceText: B E L A J A R !!!
      nextDialogueID: Hikari Bulan 6 event part 3
      moodTargetHeroine: 1
      moodChangeAmount: 3
      moneyChange: 0
      endOfMonth: 0
      triggerNormalTransition: 1
      normalTransitionText: 'Pemain dan Hikari pun belajar bareng di rumah Pemain
        walaupun mereka hanya berdua di satu rumah mereka tetap belajar dengan serius '
      requiredMoodHeroine: 0
